=== INSTALLING DJANGO ===

To get the latest official version Django first
download Django-1.5.1.tar.gz (https://www.djangoproject.com/download/1.5.1/tarball/). Then:

tar xzvf Django-1.5.1.tar.gz
cd Django-1.5.1
sudo python setup.py install

You can also use pip:

pip install Django==1.5.1


=== RUN SERVER ===

To run server in debug mode, simple run:

python manage.py runserver
